@baseUrl = https://localhost:5001
@adminEmail = admin@hotel.com
@adminPassword = Admin123!
@accessToken = 

### ===============================
### AUTHENTICATION ENDPOINTS
### ===============================

### Admin Login - Get JWT Token
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{adminEmail}}",
  "password": "{{adminPassword}}"
}

###

### Register New Guest User
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "John Doe",
  "email": "john.doe@example.com",
  "password": "SecurePass123!"
}

###

### Refresh Access Token
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "your-refresh-token-here"
}

###

### ===============================
### ROOM TYPE ENDPOINTS (Admin Only)
### ===============================

### Get All Room Types
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/roomtypes
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### Create Room Type
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/roomtypes
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Deluxe Suite",
  "description": "Luxury room with ocean view and private balcony"
}

###

### Get Room Type by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/roomtypes/1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### Update Room Type
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/roomtypes/1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Deluxe Suite",
  "description": "Updated luxury room description"
}

###

### Delete Room Type
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/roomtypes/1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### ===============================
### ROOM ENDPOINTS (Admin Only)
### ===============================

### Get All Rooms
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/rooms
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### Create Room
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/rooms
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "roomNumber": "101",
  "floor": 1,
  "pricePerNight": "150.00",
  "roomTypeId": 1
}

###

### Get Room by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/rooms/1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### Update Room
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/rooms/1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "roomNumber": "101",
  "floor": 1,
  "pricePerNight": "160.00",
  "roomTypeId": 1
}

###

### Delete Room
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/rooms/1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### ===============================
### RESERVATION ENDPOINTS
### ===============================

### Get All Reservations (Admin/Receptionist)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reservations
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### Get Own Reservations (Guest)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reservations/my
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### Get Reservation by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reservations/1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### Create Reservation (Guest)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/reservations
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "roomId": 1,
  "checkInDate": "2024-12-20",
  "checkOutDate": "2024-12-23"
}

###

### Update Reservation (Admin/Receptionist)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/reservations/1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "Confirmed",
  "isPaid": true
}

###

### Cancel Reservation (Admin/Receptionist)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/reservations/1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### ===============================
### GUEST PROFILE ENDPOINTS
### ===============================

### Get Own Profile (Guest)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/guestprofiles/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### Get Profile by ID (Admin/Receptionist)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/guestprofiles/1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### Create/Update Guest Profile (Guest)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/guestprofiles
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phoneNumber": "+1-555-0123",
  "address": "123 Main St, New York, NY 10001",
  "nationalId": "123-45-6789"
}

###

### ===============================
### HANGFIRE DASHBOARD
### ===============================

### Access Hangfire Dashboard (Admin only, requires browser)
GET {{baseUrl}}/hangfire
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###
